    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The party has accepted the invitation of the late Baroness Fossilthwaite, challenging them to complete a “silly game” in order to inherit her once-grand manor house. The clock is ticking, and the stakes are high – can the Mages stop the clock by midnight to claim their prize? Bring your wits and your weapons for this puzzle-packed escape-room-meets-dungeon crawler adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This adventure is perfect for Level 3 Mages, but you can also rebalance encounters as needed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Content Warnings: </strong>Descriptions of monsters, rats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>INCLUDES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5-Session Adventure (sessions last ~90 min) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Master Guide that makes this adventure easy to run, with limited prep</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Animated* Environments (5 Variants)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Battlemaps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 Creatures/Monsters (2 Variants)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 Music Track</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 Soundscape</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 Sound Effects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 Inventory Items</p></li></ul>",
